column9: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2019
column14: I love these! The quality is great. The key chains are nice but I absolutely love the chapstick holders. I have one on my work bag, one on my daughter's backpack, one on my diaper bag and one in my car. It is so convenient not to have to dig around for your chapstick. It's great for my daughter too, she would always lose it, now she has access to it whenever needed.

column9: Reviewed in the United States on October 25, 2019
column14: The quality I paid for is there . I love them  ! I won’t ever pay more than how much I did here for them . But Etsy had them for 5 dollars each so I got a steal ! And they match my steering wheel cover perfect ! Delivery was perfect ! They are cheap but that’s what you get and you get them at a good price but even being cheap I’m impressed! And I loved reading the reviews so I’m making one

column9: Reviewed in the United States on August 11, 2020
column14: These work for generic standard chapstick, but are too slim for EOS chapstick wands that have long caps. My first and third grader could barely push them in, and when you pull them out the wand breaks or cap gets lodged in the holder. Super cute and I'm sure they work for most people, but we use only specific products for my kids and they don't work for us.

column9: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2019
column14: I gave a couple to co-workers and they loved them as well. A nice little gift to give co-workers at a very affordable cost! I have to wear a badge at work, so the color options here are perfect to change up my badge every so often!

column9: Reviewed in the United States on April 16, 2020
column14: These are awesome, gave one set to my daughters' friend that just turned 16. One I kept for myself and one set aside for my sister's birthday, plus keeping spares to give for unexpected birthdays for my daughters' friends.

column9: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2020
column14: Bought these for my smackers obsessed child. They’re exactly as pictured a perfect fit with a little wiggle room for different sized lip balms. I love the length of the strap and the actual texture of the product. Came perfectly packaged.
